description: This API supports batching and range selection. By default it will only return first 50 images matching images.Use the {take} and {skip} parameters to control how many images to return in a given batch.

iteration_id.description: The iteration id. Defaults to workspace.

take.description: Maximum number of images to return. Defaults to 50, limited to 256.

skip.description: Number of images to skip before beginning the image batch. Defaults to 0.

message.description: A message explaining the error reported by the service.
